::Dark Prime::

     "All I want," Dark Prime said looking at the two. "Is to take 
down the Alliance. I hate to think of what they could do if they ever 
get back to Cybertron. It could be desimated. That is what I am doing 
out here. I am going to meet with the group known as the Destrons and 
see if they will help me in my quest.
     "I would like the Maximals help as well. I relized that I was 
removed of my goodness to take down the Alliance, anyway I can. The 
old Prime wouldn't have been able to do that. I belive that the 
Oracle will let me have my Goodness back after this ordeal is over. 
If I am not dead. But if I have to die to destroy the Alliance, then 
so be it, at least I will know that it was Destroyed."
     He looked the two over. What they couldn't know was that the Key 
to Vector Sigma was still on him, and since it was basically a 
program he had put into himself, secretly. Now he could shoot it from 
optic blasts.
